{"tid":1838860,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[人手置頂][行動Post]連儂牆補完計劃！人人都要做文宣！每晚十點鐘出。要人!","createTime":"2020-01-24T07:23:49.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-25T05:10:01.000Z","uid":271367,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"9c0befe26c839c492d24440ca7e975bb24ffeb4b","tid":1838860,"uid":271367,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T07:23:49.000Z","msg":"其實而家手足砌牆風險高，隔晚就俾人撕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n試過幾日都無文宣係牆，條街好似平行時空咁。唔少手足都好鬱悶。<br />\n你有無諗過<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">每晚用幾十秒時間</span></span>，就已經幫到手足。<br />\n<br />\n知你班友睇左幾行字好悶已經無耐性<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。行動重點寫係頭，想知詳情就睇落d。<br />\n<br />\n1, 所有人<span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">上Facebook follow &quot; 十點鐘出&quot;</span></span><br />\n2, <span style=\"color: orange;\">夜晚十點</span>根據每日精選提供o既Link<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">俾like</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。 <br />\n3, 俾完Like<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">再加comment，share</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<br />\n4, 每晚重覆步驟2同3推Post。<br />\n<br />\nFB: <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/Post10pm/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FPost10pm%2F&d=J5HXnbFloTEqGlUzWM3JX%2FZtcVXZMMHuQDZeBHkLh3U%3D&h=21857360\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/Post10pm/</a><br />\nTG: <a href=\"https://t.me/post10pm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fpost10pm&d=J5HXnbFloTEqGlUzWM3JX%2FZtcVXZMMHuQDZeBHkLh3U%3D&h=35d79a70\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/post10pm</a><br />\n<br />\n======================================================================<br />\n<br />\n你可能會問，連儂牆整得咁多咁靚，仲點樣補完呀？<br />\n大家要記住：連儂牆係打破圍爐既第一戰線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<br />\n好多街坊，唔同背景既人都係牆接收資訊。<br />\n如果實體既牆會俾人清，咁虛擬既牆Facebook呢？撕紙狗吹得我脹呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n只要夠人多！有隊型同時做！推post洗版，務求令到更多唔同背景唔同階層o既人睇到。<br />\n令目標資訊/文宣傳俾更多人睇。就好似十點鳩叫一樣。<br />\n<br />\n唔想俾沙士洗版！唔想俾人帶風向！<br />\n自已風向自已帶。<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">勿忘初衷！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n每晚百萬人推一單新聞，對家Fake News抹黑都無掟企<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<br />\n<br />\n呢個同其他文宣戰線一樣，要長期做。因為你永遠唔知會發生乜野事。開文宣新戰線，就可守(出士氣post)/可攻(防抹黑)。<br />\n可能你會質疑初期出既精選無乜料到，但當日子來到，你就會知呢個武器既威力。<br />\n<br />\n係呢度，要向一班低調但日日承受住高風險砌牆既手足致敬！<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">兄弟爬山，各自努力。<br />\n光復香港，時代革命。<br />\n五大訴求，缺一不可。</span></span><br />\n<br />\nFB: <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/Post10pm/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FPost10pm%2F&d=J5HXnbFloTEqGlUzWM3JX%2FZtcVXZMMHuQDZeBHkLh3U%3D&h=21857360\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/Post10pm/</a><br />\nTG: <a href=\"https://t.me/post10pm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fpost10pm&d=J5HXnbFloTEqGlUzWM3JX%2FZtcVXZMMHuQDZeBHkLh3U%3D&h=35d79a70\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/post10pm</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cdbe5cf3aa04e6a645b6e83648d37d40b13af3b2","tid":1838860,"uid":271367,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T07:24:45.000Z","msg":"今晚十點約定你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"432bddc173dc0dec3cc8a9e23c0a55520f517c79","tid":1838860,"uid":8732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"